 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EZondle is a games-based learning website that enables teachers and students to create games to support exactly their learning needs.\nTeachers and students can choose learning topics or create their own (almost all of the content on zondle is crowd-sourced). The chosen topic can then be played in any of a large and growing selection of casual games.\nUsers can also monitor progress, message their friends, customise their avatar, and create their own casual games. Teachers can also set topics to particular classes, and run reports. Zondle junior provides a protected interface, totally under the control of the teacher.\u003C/p\u003E",
